stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Ready: 消息可投递
    Ready --> Inflight: Receive/POP
    Inflight --> Committed: 业务成功且 ACK 成功
    Inflight --> WaitingRetry: 返回失败/未 ACK/处理超时
    Inflight --> WaitingRetry: 客户端宕机且不可见期到期
    WaitingRetry --> Ready: 到达重试时间
    WaitingRetry --> DLQ: 超过最大尝试次数
    Committed --> [*]
    DLQ --> [*]
